## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the rapidly changing nature of supply chain dynamics. Additionally, while the sources provide a comprehensive overview, they may not capture all regional variations in the shortage. Further research could explore the long-term impacts of these shortages on the poultry industry and consumer behavior.